Title: Mr. Jealousy
Plot: Finch is scared about Jack liking Vicki, so he sets her up to look bad, but he's not sure when she'll get him back. Meanwhile, Nina brings in a woman off the street to prove to Jack that he was wrong to hire Vicki. She is worried though when the woman gets lost in the building.
ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.
